@startuml m7-pdb-quorum-coupling-sequence
skinparam dpi 300
title M7 — PDB / maxUnavailable Coupled to BEAM Quorum

participant "Quorum\ncontroller" as QC
participant "Horde / cluster" as H
participant "K8s API\n(PDB)" as API
participant "Eviction / drain\nAPI" as EV

QC -> H: cluster size, quorum threshold,\nhandoff throughput
QC -> API: set PDB minAvailable = quorum\nmaxUnavailable = handoff capacity
== node drain ==
EV -> API: evict pod?
alt would break quorum / exceed handoff
  API --> EV: DENY (PDB)
  note over EV #ccffcc: quorum preserved
else within budget
  API --> EV: ALLOW
  EV -> H: handoff; proceed
end
@enduml
